<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Kubernetes App</title>
  <style>
    /* ===========================
       Global
       =========================== */
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f9fc;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: #1f2937;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #2563eb;
    }

    /* ===========================
       Header
       =========================== */
    header {
      background-color: #2d3748;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    header p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      color: #a0aec0;
    }

    /* ===========================
       Container
       =========================== */
    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }

    h2 {
      color: #1d4ed8;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #93c5fd;
      padding-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    ul li {
      background: #e0f2fe;
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #0369a1;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    p {
      background: #fef3c7;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-left: 4px solid #fbbf24;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 1rem 0;
      color: #92400e;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
      background-color: #16a34a;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 6px;
      transition: background 0.2s;
      margin-top: 1rem;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #15803d;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 3rem 0 1rem 0;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Bienvenue <%= user %> </h1>
    <p>Projet pédagogique Kubernetes — Node.js / PostgreSQL / Redis</p>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <h2>Architecture</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Node.js (Express)</li>
      <li>PostgreSQL (StatefulSet)</li>
      <li>Redis (ReplicaSet)</li>
      <li>Kubernetes (Orchestration)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Sécurité</h2>
    <p>
      - Mots de passe hashés avec bcrypt<br>
      - Secrets gérés via Kubernetes Secrets<br>
      - Cache Redis avec TTL pour optimiser les performances
    </p>

    <a class="btn" href="/users">Voir les utilisateurs</a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2026 - Projet Kubernetes DevOps
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
